libredblack
------------------------------------------
RedBlack Balanced Tree Searching and Sorting Library

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  libredblack-devel-1.3-1bl7
  libredblack0-1.3-1bl7
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1
  python39-3.9.16-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2
  python39-3.9.16-1

Canonical website:
  https://sourceforge.net/projects/libredblack/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/libredblack/libredblack-1.3.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libredblack-1.3-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libredblack-1.3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libredblack-1.3-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libredblack-1.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libredblack0-1.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libredblack-devel-1.3-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

